dcterms:description: A dataset containing U.S. election statistics, where nodes represent U.S. counties and edges connect adjacent counties. The dataset is used for regression tasks involving various election-related statistics.

dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of a page-page network of Wikipedia pages, where nodes represent pages and edges reflect mutual hyperlinks. The dataset is used for predicting page visit traffic.
